description: The NASDAQ 100 Index aims to reflect the performance of the following market: 100 of the largest American and global non-financial equities listed on the NASDAQ Stock Market Weighted by free-float adjusted market capitalisation Reviewed on an annual basis and rebalanced on an at least a quarterly basis Additional information on the index, selection and weighting methodology is available at https://www.indexes.nasdaqomx.com
name: Xtrackers NASDAQ 100 UCITS ETF 1C
